name: Transcicada
text: If this card is Special Summoned: You can Special Summon 1 "Moult Token" (Insect/EARTH/Level 3/ATK 0/DEF 0). While the Token Special Summoned by this effect is on the field, you cannot Special Summon monsters from the Extra Deck, except Insect monsters. You can only use this effect of "Transcicada" once per turn.
